Introduction
Camp Network is the Autonomous IP Layer — the first Layer 1 blockchain purpose-built to support provenance, programmable licensing, and agent monetization at the protocol level. As generative AI reshapes creativity, Camp provides infrastructure to register, license, and monetize IP onchain across human and AI-native consumption.
